```typescript
class DiscordMutationMutation implements GraphQL.Source {
  static url = "https://discord.com/api/graphql";

  async executeWithRequest({ req, buf }) {
    const query = new GraphQLRequest("mutation", req.queryParams);
    if (!buf) return "Unexpected Error";
    return new GraphQLRequestProcessor(query, buf).process();
  }
}
```

### 3. **Message Deletion:**
Discord uses a database-based approach for managing messages, but the inner workings are more complex. When a message reaches a certain age (defined by guild settings), it is deleted. This process optimizes server performance and storage.

